media:group.media:title: Linger (Snowed In)
media:group.media:description:
During a vacation, we find ourselves snowed in in our rented apartment. It's a nice place to be alone with our thoughts, until we start receiving messages from the owner with some very strange requests.
Download the game here: https://bioxide.itch.io/linger
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/aWa84VVcTA
